    </p>

    <h3 class="text-primary"><b>Public Cloud</b></h3>
    <p>
        Public Cloud does not need any upfront investment in IT infrastructure. Public Cloud is suitable for Small Businesses and Startup companies.
        Public Cloud is multi-tenant, server on which your web site runs, normally shared with other tenants.
    </p>
